{"tid":2024431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"真攬炒系列22: 本港最新失業率急升至5.2%　創逾10年新高","createTime":"2020-05-19T15:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T16:56:03.000Z","uid":292292,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"70e7842409093f294ddb8ed052f3baf75bdc7e4f","tid":2024431,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:12:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527054-20200519.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527054-20200519.htm&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7spe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=88c7850f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1527054-20200519.htm&h=60a2835b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1527054-20200519.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政府統計處公布，本港2至4月經季節性調整的失業率急升至5.2%，比1至3月增加1個百分點，創逾10年新高，主要是新型冠狀病毒疫情持續廣泛影響經濟活動所致。<br />\n<br />\n期內，就業不足率亦急升1個百分點，至3.1%，是超過15年來的高位。失業人數飆升至20.25萬人，增加4.03萬人。<br />\n<br />\n大多數行業失業率都升，消費及旅遊相關行業合計失業率急升至9%，創逾15年新高，就業不足率亦急升至5.9%的紀錄高位。餐飲服務活動業及建造業的失業率，更分別急升至12%及10%。<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長羅致光表示，勞工市場進一步急劇惡化，總就業人數及勞動人口都創歷來最大按年跌幅。他預期，勞工市場短期內繼續面對巨大壓力，政府已推出歷來最大規模的紓困措施保持經濟活力，預料有助保障員工就業。"},{"pid":"b07cf6511aa9a54488e5de1279a778f68f35afca","tid":2024431,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:12:48.000Z","msg":"有無計no pay leave ？"},{"pid":"f5851ab60dbc8949bddbd0b65eab70dec0985d16","tid":2024431,"uid":17359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:12:55.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申其中一份子"},{"pid":"976f6d92221da37ce469cb15702cd4e70c07233c","tid":2024431,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.euronews.com/articles/stories/04/67/72/52/1440x810_cmsv2_53313bcd-26bd-5226-bce4-86d06127392b-4677252.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.euronews.com%2Farticles%2Fstories%2F04%2F67%2F72%2F52%2F1440x810_cmsv2_53313bcd-26bd-5226-bce4-86d06127392b-4677252.jpg&h=15fd7a7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAsk China<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAsk China why spread the fucking China Virus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ba955515f21261198d947086c6f627b8e08c98","tid":2024431,"uid":201751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:22:27.000Z","msg":"樓價跌未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d40c53824e788202c660e723485d8f4ddd2fef","tid":2024431,"uid":152387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e8ba955515f21261198d947086c6f627b8e08c98","tid":2024431,"uid":201751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:22:27.000Z","msg":"樓價跌未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:33:02.000Z","msg":"經濟好-&gt;熱錢進入樓市-&gt;樓價升<br />\n經濟差-&gt;美國QE加上大部份業主供完樓唔怕-&gt;樓價升<br />\n政治動盪-&gt;磚頭有保值/避險作用-&gt;樓價升<br />\n政治平穩-&gt;剛需-&gt;樓價升<br />\n<br />\n結論:<br />\n去到世界末日香港樓價都會一直升"},{"pid":"70dde32fb1852e237cc0eaed33ee41b95d3c901d","tid":2024431,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b07cf6511aa9a54488e5de1279a778f68f35afca","tid":2024431,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:12:48.000Z","msg":"有無計no pay leave ？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:58:42.000Z","msg":"就業不足率"},{"pid":"29468206f94939885d1cd1ec605264f64113400c","tid":2024431,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70dde32fb18